{"tid":2113283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍雙航母南海軍演　環球時報總編：中国一定能在家門口打敗美國！","createTime":"2020-07-18T04:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T05:12:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8e64ef4e3912facac30cc5b5a3471ba4e78bc06e","tid":2113283,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5012/d5012200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5012%2Fd5012200.jpg&h=0b3b37d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美軍尼米茲號、雷根號航空母艦在南海操演。（圖／達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n中美關係越發緊繃，美國派出雙航母在南海軍演。對於雙方是否會開戰，環球時報總編輯胡錫進表示，如果真的有那一天，根本不用擔心，接招就是，「我們一定能夠在家門口打敗美國」。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進17日在微博發文，對於中美是否會發生戰爭的看法，目前中美戰略互信幾乎消失殆盡，美國又加強在中國周邊的軍事，雙方發生軍事摩擦風險比以往增加，以和平方式控制的難度也加大了。<br />\n<br />\n「從理性而言，中美都不想彼此走向軍事衝突。」胡錫進分析，兩軍都在針對最壞的情況進行準備，但沒有走向軍事攤牌的戰略意願；而且中國熱愛和平，不會去太平洋深處、印度洋挑戰美國的利益，是謹慎的大國。<br />\n<br />\n但是胡錫進也強調，中國對核心利益的定義非常克制，它們都在中國家門口，但若是在家門口被嚴重軍事挑釁、強加戰爭，「在家門口為了核心利益打敗它，無論我們的戰爭動員能力，資源投入能力，還是戰鬥到底的意志，都是美國比不了的。我相信，華盛頓對此比我們還清楚」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200718/1763640.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200718%2F1763640.htm&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiYc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=2692b43f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200718/1763640.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c4ffee582a983eaa75696686fc702d2b95c94615","tid":2113283,"uid":4396,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"酸儒，不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c174730a738a208ef31f454ff68f62f4bbc7bffd","tid":2113283,"uid":3161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:20:21.000Z","msg":"快d 打啦.jpg"},{"pid":"ce9300af5e737a0015653ffd56294583c49d1086","tid":2113283,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c311a50f51957b0790436fc51d807014e28b9aaf","tid":2113283,"uid":45607,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06j64BJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06j64BJ.jpg&h=726f104e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"218a1ce1738c77b2d23186c0e00c39c981d1ef46","tid":2113283,"uid":80724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"煩撚完未，條撚樣日日出聲鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6451edb2e75cb225f5d14b25a5844d8ef234347","tid":2113283,"uid":251009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"218a1ce1738c77b2d23186c0e00c39c981d1ef46","tid":2113283,"uid":80724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"煩撚完未，條撚樣日日出聲鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:23:32.000Z","msg":"報紙日日有，係日日有人po上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b889cf142dd21a419aaf3a57a341bb317b3ba430","tid":2113283,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"射石頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c565a951d4097358e558843b5567b0f5fe89ab23","tid":2113283,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:27:15.000Z","msg":"恰到上門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc2e6e8062ead486050522b70eb2777d989db7a","tid":2113283,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"218a1ce1738c77b2d23186c0e00c39c981d1ef46","tid":2113283,"uid":80724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"r